7dc7de75f208275cc8786ff3817","tid":1368210,"uid":36920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:52:34.000Z","msg":"感動到毛管棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0eb49ab65bf858929698aae3a20b148a619007c","tid":1368210,"uid":135334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"「港台連線」西門町驚現香港連儂牆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1367035/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1367035/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f60276652dde6d2b18e81569ae1ec71b3b57c324","tid":1368210,"uid":157777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"台灣人對香港人既支持<br />\n我系台灣exchange 果陣 完全感受到<br />\n亦被感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝台灣"},{"pid":"2530955c61567a273a8d0bf804ac1941e547c590","tid":1368210,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:57:16.000Z","msg":"推啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf38ec35a2407006a890e82454e1919678a1d97a","tid":1368210,"uid":274537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"自行補上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTw2mfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTw2mfH.jpg&h=7519b4f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b240649e3e1107504543bcdf814c1088eac3219","tid":1368210,"uid":230672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:03:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c631cd947aba38db419c4fc1fb2071bd8eba10ff","tid":1368210,"uid":288527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18ccd340b90c380de8bb404743e0284b9bdadb6","tid":1368210,"uid":288527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T12:23:28.000Z","msg":"大家好，我是國立台灣大學的學生，也是這次台大學生證聲援活動召集人。<br />\n<br />\n  《逃犯條例》修訂與台灣淵源甚深。港府籍口陳同佳案打算大開司法門戶以致兩百萬人上街，而警察多次過份使用武力。但勇敢的香港人並沒有退縮，多次以Be Water方式抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n  這一個多月以來，發生了許多事，不管是數名義士自殺成仁；進入立法會並不破壞公物；地鐵站上留下零錢保護義士；集資登報國際頭條，這些高尚行為感動著全世界。<br />\n<br />\n  而在7/21，香港警察在上環前線開了數十槍，又在天橋上直接開槍射向人群。更痛心的是，途經元朗地鐵站的一般乘客被黑幫進行無差別的恐怖襲擊、港鐵刻意停站開車門、警察刻意放任黑幫並拒絕行使公權力義務，而至今政府、特首、警方依然沒有正面回應，香港一度陷入恐懼當中。<br />\n<br />\n  台大學生曾自發性地在總圖書館、傅鐘前舉行反送中活動，而7/21後，網路上亦有多名政府單位員工以匿名的方式支持香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n  因此，我們收集了大家的學生證照片，支持明天7/27光復元朗行動，並再次一起聲援：<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n 召集人 國立台灣大學歷史系某學生 敬上<br />\n<br />\n台大生號召反送中 上千人齊聚傅鐘挺香港民眾【圖輯】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906145006.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201906145006.aspx&d=0Lcuuml91xlF79uKCzc07sWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=7f181e96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201906145006.aspx</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzG53eY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzG53eY.jpg&h=9ed736bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65eO01D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65eO01D.jpg&h=15d38969&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeC5iOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHeC5iOm.jpg&h=4d75e00a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HP7H5tn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHP7H5tn.jpg&h=c41a2463&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1c8gqtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1c8gqtn.jpg&h=ca31aa3d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dmRemJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dmRemJ.jpg&h=00115028&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SvVF1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SvVF1K.jpg&h=378faedb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hVgmBz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna